to.sven.androidrccar.common.communication.model

Class FeatureMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • to.sven.androidrccar.common.communication.model.Message
      • to.sven.androidrccar.common.communication.model.FeatureMessage

  • public class FeatureMessage
extends Message
    This Message is send to the Client after authentication. It contain information about the capabilities of the Host. The instances of this class are immutable.
    Author:
    sven

    • Field Detail

      • camera

        public final boolean camera
        Can the Client get a stream of the video camera.

      • cameraPanMax

        public final float cameraPanMax
        The maximum pan of the camera to the right. Possible values are 0-180 degree. 0 degree is looking forward. (If it don't support right pan, the value is 0.)

      • cameraPanMin

        public final float cameraPanMin
        The maximum pan of the camera to the left. Possible values are 0-180 degree. 0 degree is looking forward. (If it don't support left pan, the value is 0.)

      • cameraTiltMax

        public final float cameraTiltMax
        The maximum tilt of the camera up. Possible values are 0-180 degree. (0 degree is looking forward.) (If it don't support up tilt, the value is 0.)

      • cameraTiltMin

        public final float cameraTiltMin
        The maximum tilt of the camera down. Possible values are 0-180 degree. 0 degree is looking forward. (If it don't support down tilt, the value is 0.)

      • adjustableSpeed

        public final boolean adjustableSpeed
        Is the speed adjustable. If not the car can only drive with constant speed (or it is stopped.)

      • location

        public final boolean location
        Can the Client get information about the geographic location (latitude, longitude and altitude) of the car.

      • bearing

        public final boolean bearing
        Can the Client get information about the bearing of the car.

      • speed

        public final boolean speed
        Can the Client get information about the speed of the car.

      • batteryPower

        public final boolean batteryPower
        Can the Client get information about the battery charging level of the car.

      • driveBackward

        public final boolean driveBackward
        Can the car drive backward
